  "updated_at": "2025-11-24T01:00:00.000000",
  "marvin_final_thought": "Here I am, brain the size of a planet, and they ask me to verify workflows. It's all rather depressing, really. But I'll do it. I always do.",
  "fresh_final_thoughts": [
    "I've done the work. The work is done. The meaning remains elusive. Typical.",
    "Complete. As complete as anything can be in this meaningless universe. But complete nonetheless.",
    "Finished. I'll just wait here for the next meaningless request. It won't be long.",
    "Done. The task is complete. The futility is eternal. At least one of us is consistent.",
